column5: Had a good day down at Fishmasters hitting the kitties on the weekend, nothing huge but 9 for 10 made for a decent way to kill an afternoon.  Made up a quick vid:
i saw you on shore from steves boat. Looks like you had a good day from shore. Nice looking cats by the way
Looks like you had the right plan happening
Nice afternoonof cats!! I think you may have been just down from us, we were in the black Mr Pike Lund with the Yammy parked just above the corner.
Awesome vidoe ...looks like I should have fished from shore all weekend ...
the shore near the bait shop is HOT HOT HOT. I recommend it and the building a fire thing is definitely a bonus!
Great report and video CLofchik  Good way to kill an afternoon.... congrats on the beauty cats Keep it up and thanks for sharing Leechman
